    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Symptoms can be present 2-6 days after rapid correction of serum sodium\nDysarthria\nDysphagia\nLethargy\nBehavioral disturbances/ confusion\nParaparesis\nor quadriparesis\nSeizures\n\"Locked in\" syndrome\nComa\nand\ndeath",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
